th a\nTwoFactorAuditQueryService that aggregates counts and projects user\nrows directly via JdbcTemplate. Avoids hydrating User entities and\ntheir lazy userRoles collections, so a single privileged call no\nlonger pulls the full user-role-group graph into memory.\n\n- countByType(): one GROUP BY against userinfo\n- countPrivileged(): single join over userrolemembers + userroleauthorities\n  with a FILTER aggregate for the missing-2FA subset\n- count(filter) / list(filter, offset, limit): conditional WHERE built\n  from status + type filters, paged DB-side with LIMIT/OFFSET\n\nThe list endpoint now returns a standard DHIS2 Pager wrapper and\naccepts ?page, ?pageSize, ?paging=false. Default pageSize=50, max=1000.\n\nMirrors the JdbcStatisticsProvider pattern already used in\ndhis-service-administration.\n\nAI Assisted.","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"73a19046f89cc2f6c79d93c9c0909d199d3ed548","tree_id":"3620d025f93e0903f33d8cfdc4aa114764b93a1e","timestamp":"2026-05-22T21:30:06Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/d